code: /**  * Invoke {@link TestContextManager#prepareTestInstance(Object)} and  * then evaluate the next {@link Statement} in the execution chain  * (typically an instance of {@link RunAfterTestMethodCallbacks}).  */ @Override public void evaluate() throws Throwable {     this.testContextManager.prepareTestInstance(this.testInstance).     this.next.evaluate(). }
